<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Devis signé — GestoPro</title>
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f3f4f6; margin: 0; padding: 40px 16px; color: #111827; }
        .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08); overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background: #1e293b; padding: 20px 28px; }
        .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; }
        .header h1 span { color: #60a5fa; }
        .body { padding: 36px 32px; text-align: center; }
        .icon { font-size: 52px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        h2 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 22px; color: #15803d; }
        p { color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 8px; }
        .box { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 20px; margin-top: 24px; text-align: left; }
        .row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #d1fae5; }
        .row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .lbl { color: #6b7280; }
        .val { font-weight: 500; color: #111827; }
        .footer { background: #f8fafc; padding: 16px 28px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header"><h1>Gesto<span>Pro</span></h1></div>
    <div class="body">
        <div class="icon">✅</div>
        <h2>Devis signé avec succès</h2>
        <p>Votre signature a bien été enregistrée.</p>
        <p>{{ quote.user.fullName }} a été notifié de votre acceptation.</p>

        <div class="box">
            <div class="row">
                <span class="lbl">Devis</span>
                <span class="val">{{ quote.number }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <span class="lbl">Signé le</span>
                <span class="val">{{ quote.signedAt|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <span class="lbl">Montant TTC</span>
                <span class="val" style="color:#2563eb;font-weight:700;">{{ quote.totalTtc|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} {{ quote.currency }}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">GestoPro — Signature électronique horodatée</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
